window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A wizard lord bent on conquest. Mythical creatures return and threaten the lands. A foreboding future awaits.</p> <p>Thrones lie vacant while a power-hungry wizard lord seeks world domination.&nbsp;Armed with unequaled power, who can stop his mad lust for conquest?</p> <p>Monsters from legend arise and stalk the land.&nbsp;Who or what is behind their return?</p> <p>The Seers of Kelmar, a reclusive sect of prophets, claim the future has become obscured from their visions.&nbsp;What foreboding future awaits the Eight Wizardoms?</p> <p>A band of reluctant heroes embark on a quest to stop the chaos sweeping over the Eight Wizardoms.&nbsp;Can they prevent the end of their world?</p> <p><i>Temple of the Oracle </i>is the third entry in Fate of Wizardoms, a thrilling epic-fantasy saga from best-selling author Jeffrey L. Kohanek.</p>"; 
